posting_body: ['The Olivian', '809 Olive Way , Seattle, WA, 98101', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 98', 'OR Text', '98', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'Finer City Living', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1916 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'There are few buildings with the renown and prominence the Olivian holds.', "It's easy to see why.", 'Our residents enjoy top quality amenities, excellence of service, large floorplans, and high end finishes in a downtown setting.', 'We offer convenience, service, luxury, and a prized home experience.', 'In total, we offer 24 different floorplans.', 'If you like what you see but want more options with us, call or email to learn about availability in your timeline.', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet policy: We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $500 deposit per pet (refundable).', 'Pet rent is $40 for cats and $65 for dogs.', 'Please contact our leasing office for more information about our Parking Policy.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday-Wednesday:9:00AM-7:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'WoHz9Hr1WLJv']
